                        <h3 class="text-theme-colored mt-0 pt-5">What we do</h3>
                        <p class="mb-20">ODH Foundation aims to provide a platform for Indian artists to showcase their talent and take their work to a wider audience through events. We are securing the future of endangered art forms by providing livelihood opportunities to traditional artists and craftsmen, ensuring that their work remains viable. We also support efforts to pass on India's cultural heritage to future generations. We are working to make Indian arts and culture more relevant to youth and help them appreciate and connect with their extraordinary heritage.</p>


